<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦١٦٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3645">أَبِي الزِّنَادِ، </a>عَنِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3424">الْأَعْرَجِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> رَأَى رَجُلًا يَسُوقُ بَدَنَةً،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ لَهُ:</span> ارْكَبْهَا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> يَا رَسُولَ اللهِ، إِنَّهَا بَدَنَةٌ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ارْكَبْهَا، وَيْلَكَ، فِي الثَّانِيَةِ أَوْ فِي الثَّالِثَةِ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>